data.description: **New roof to be installed prior to closing.** Fantastic home in sought-after Oakleaf Plantation! This 4 bd 2 ba  home w/ bonus room will give you 2,368 sq ft of generous space to move about. Open floor plan great for entertaining & family gatherings. Cozy living area up front with living/ dining combo. Your kitchen w/ 42'' cabinets, granite countertops, SS appliances overlooks the great room w/ high ceilings, wood-like tile throughout most areas. The primary bathroom is fully equipped w/ a separate tub & shower, double sinks, & plenty of under sink storage. Finally, the backyard, a great space for entertaining & enjoying the outdoors. Enjoy all that Oakleaf Plantation has to offer- Resort amenities w/ the pools, club house, fitness center, activities for everyone. Shopping, movie theaters, restaurants & the easy access to SR 23.
